 ï§ At least a basic understanding of how both ICO\u2019s (or TGE\u2019s) and bounty campaigns work ï§ Knowledge of influencer marketing, affiliate marketing & outreach ï§ Able & willing to dedicate 20-30 hours/week to this job, with the possibility of transitioning to full-time hours in the future. You should also be able to make yourself available at different times of the day in order to accommodate dealing with others in different time zones. ï§ Motivated & Comfortable working remotely ï§ A \u2018hands-on\u2019 approach, desire to take initiative & set your own goals to maximize results ï§ Be ready to invoice AmaZix for your services ï§ Be comfortable being paid in Ethereum ï§ Be organized and ready to bring your skills into a decentralized organization with members from many different countries To apply: To show that you have the required skills (or to show you can learn them quickly), please answer the following: 1. Explain in your own words what an ICO or TGE is. 2. Explain in your own words what a bounty campaign is. 3. What is Ethereum Gas and how is it used? 4. Please provide the token contract address of Bancor. Please do not reach out via Telegram or other channels for the job posting. We have a large backlog of applicants and it could take up to a few weeks to respond. Ability to follow instructions is important. Please submit your application (including answers to the above questions) to [emailÂ protected] Skills ico, marketing, outreach Compensation TBD Applications for this job are currently closed. "
